  <p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px; color: #ffffff; font-family: 'Roboto Condensed', sans-serif;">SHIELD did not hold a premine. Our development team is run solely on donations.</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; color: #ffffff; font-family: 'Roboto Condensed', sans-serif; background-color: #000000;" /><span style="color: #ffffff; font-family: 'Roboto Condensed', sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">If you are interested in the SHIELD project and want to help, you can donate to any one of the following wallet addresses. Your support is greatly appreciated.</span></p>
